  "title": "DRIVER",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Possess valid class 4/5 Driving licence and able to handle heavy load of goods</li>\n  <li>work hard and follow arrangements and company regulations</li>\n  <li>Safely transporting workers as well as various products and materials to and from specified locations in a timely manner</li>\n  <li>Assisting with the loading and offloading of materials.</li>\n  <li>Ensuring that the company vehicle is always parked in areas that permit parking to avoid towing / fines.</li>\n  <li>Keeping the company vehicle clean and properly maintained by performing regular washing, cleaning, and vehicle maintenance</li>\n  <li>Reporting any accidents and vehicle damage to management</li>\n  <li>Good working attitude and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Willing to work in a construction site with general worker also if driving work is in rest</li>\n  <li>must available for 24/7</li>\n  <li>With basic mechanics knowledge preferrable.</li>\n</ul>",
